data.description: PRICE INPROVEMENT*SELLERS WILL CONSIDER ALL REASONABLE OFFERS* Elegant home with a PANORAMIC COUNTRYSIDE VIEW situated on a landscaped acre in the highly desirable CANYON WEST GOLF COURSE COMMUNITY & BROCK ISD.  Enjoy SUNSETS on the extended back porch overlooking the professionally installed KOI POND with relaxing waterfall sounds. An 8 ft. iron door leads to an ample foyer with the formal dining situated on the left and the office with French doors on the right. Handsome hand scraped hardwood floors flow through the entry, office, living & dining. A wall of windows bathes the spacious living area in natural light and frames the PICTURESQUE VIEW. DOUBLE OVENS, 5 BURNER GAS COOK TOP, ISLAND &  WALK IN PANTRY IS A CHEF'S DREAM. Spacious primary bedroom with luxurious en-suite bath features dual vanities, walk in shower, jetted tub & the walk in closet of your dreams that's attached to the utility room. Jack & Jill bath between two bedrooms and an additional full bath for bedroom 2.
